        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this function is considered medium. This assessment is based on the typical operations involved in evaluating billing records, which include conditional logic and data validation. The function's complexity is influenced by the specific criteria it uses to classify billing records, which involve multiple checks or conditions."
        }
